body.text: This library queries some of the data available on http://seattle.data.gov.
We are using your current location for this example. Remember that this data is located in the Seattle area in Washington state.
The emergency 911 calls action returns the latest 911 calls. All the query APIs support paging, 0 is the start index and 50 is the number of elements.
Returns the latest 911 calls in the Seattle area
Returns the list of SDOT traffic cameras in the Seattle area
Creates a circle filter near a location
Queries a view and filters by location
Returns the list of neighborhood structures in the Seattle area
Returns the list of neighborhood structures in the Seattle area
